{"title":"柴屋灯火——致《共产党宣言》的第一个中译者陈望道先生","authors":["张含贞"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":12,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"柴屋灯火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——致《共产党宣言》的第一个中译者陈望道先生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张含贞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回到故乡一九二○年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他擦亮柴屋的油灯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星辉融入窗棂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这种穿骨入髓的巨响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从黑暗浓重的深处"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磅礴迤来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先生的双手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不敢丝毫放松"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柴屋的灯火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"透开理想的光芒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"质朴的声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行云流水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光荣的铁锤和镰刀结合"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指明历史行程"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"结满蛛网的柴屋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生动的眼眸炯炯如神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命的树　真理的树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"葱茏迭翠叶叶常青"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我抚摸这一角大洋的经典著作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火焰灼灼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"号角的力量"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"势如破竹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重雾也难堵塞＊"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}